  <brief_title>Effects of Linagliptin on Left Ventricular Myocardial DYsfunction in Patients With Type 2 DiAbetes Mellitus and Concentric Left Ventricular Geometry</brief_title>
  <acronym>DYDA2</acronym>
  <official_title>Effects of the Dipeptidyl Peptidase-4 (DPP-4) Inhibitor Linagliptin on Left Ventricular Myocardial DYsfunction in Patients With Type 2 DiAbetes Mellitus and Concentric Left Ventricular Geometry</official_title>
